location.fullValue: Desert Spoon Plan, Parkside at Anthem at Merrill Ranch

data.description: Welcome to this adorable 2-bedroom home located in the dynamic adult Community of Anthem at Merrill Ranch! Featuring a 2-car garage, mature shade trees, and stone accents. Discover the spaciousness of a great room floor plan offering tile flooring in all the right places. The sliders leading to the covered patio & inviting backyard make your indoor-outdoor living a breeze. Kitchen offers recessed lighting, granite counters, cabinetry w/crown moulding, and a 2-tiered breakfast bar. Carpeting in bedrooms only. The primary bedroom boasts a bay window and large walk-in closet. The primary bathroom offers dual sink and a large shower w/ glass doors& grab bars. The luscious backyard is the perfect spot to relax. Come see it today and start living the resort lifestyle now!
